The '''''Sluissi Wanderlust''''' was a [[Passenger liner/Legends|starliner]] carrying 323 refugees to [[Kwilaan Starport/Legends|Kwilaan Starport]], [[Naboo/Legends|Naboo]], in [[22 BBY/Legends|22 BBY]]. After being detained in a holding pattern for four hours by the ''[[Pickaxe]]'', it was redirected to [[Theed/Legends|Theed]].

